      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Ciclo Report Program : Livello di dettaglio               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-liv-det-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di interruzione forzata    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero records scritti               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-scr-000      thru inc-rec-scr-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record del prodotto                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-fso-rdp-000      thru cmp-fso-rdp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda del tipo esecuzione        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tip-exe           =    01
                     go to prn-liv-det-100
           else if   rr-tip-exe           =    02
                     go to prn-liv-det-200.
       prn-liv-det-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo esecuzione : simulazione in stampa         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se righe residue sufficienti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-res                >    1
                     go to prn-liv-det-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Intestazione pagina                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-ini-cic-999.
       prn-liv-det-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Interlinea                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa record del prodotto                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      132                  to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      001                  to   p-pos                  .
           move      w-rdp                to   p-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-999.
       prn-liv-det-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo esecuzione : generazione definitiva        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura record del prodotto in file se-   *
      *                  * quenziale in output                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione carattere di fine record   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-scr-fso-cfr        to   w-rdp-chr-end          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Scrittura record                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rdp                to   g-rec                  .
           move      "PN"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvout"
                                         using g                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-999.
       prn-liv-det-999.
           exit.

