           move      s-mes                to   w-scr-fso-mes          .
           move      s-gio                to   w-scr-fso-gio          .
           move      w-scr-fso-dat        to   w-rdt-dec-lst          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione listino                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rr-cod-lst-des       to   w-rdt-des-lst          .
